title: Green Break Vegan Restaurant
typeOfFood: Vegan, Organic, Western, Fast food, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Spanish
description: Little cafe with some counter seating offering vegan take away, opened Dec 2013 by the owners of former Green Break Vegan Shop in Madrid. Offers all vegan food such as Spanish omelet, burritos, burgers, waffles, smoothies, raw food, and cakes. Beverages include organic coffee, wine and beer. Free Wi-Fi.
